epic.network

Class ContactNetwork<V extends broadwick.graph.Vertex,E extends broadwick.graph.Edge<V>>

  • java.lang.Object
    • epic.network.ContactNetwork<V,E>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    broadwick.graph.Graph<V,E>, Serializable

    public class ContactNetwork<V extends broadwick.graph.Vertex,E extends broadwick.graph.Edge<V>>
extends Object
implements broadwick.graph.Graph<V,E>
    ContactNetwork is an undirected graph. This class is the undirected version of broadwick.graph.DirectedGraph but it also contains methods to initialise with certain common network shapes
